Commentary Text: Hazlewood to Karthik, out Caught by Dhoni!! Top spot from Dhoni. Many thought it was bat onto the ground and then to Dhoni, but Dhoni put out an appeal immediately. Umpire Chris Gaffaney was convinced there was an edge, but it was too tight for him to see if it didn't hit the ground. So took help from the man in the AC box and the replay clearly showing that this yorker hit the ground, took the edge and went straight to Dhoni. Hazlewood bowled the yorker, DK tried to squeeze it to third man and guided it to Dhoni. Karthik c Dhoni b Hazlewood 26(11) [4s-3 6s-1]
